{"tid":1535113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月逢星期六揸春袋","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:54:29.000Z","uid":167355,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3bea6d8ac4af28b03c992181f7af93ac51aadc43","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ujEkZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ujEkZQ.png&h=6ac2e4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n其實9月1既賽後檢討都覺得損失低 又做到目的<br />\n我地係要諗離開路段 <br />\n但謹記去度機場只有2樣野 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一係遊客 一係排巴士離開</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好走去東涌啊 豬仔 <br />\n一陣馬路大搜捕真係救你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ounKy0x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FounKy0x.png&h=3a638d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你話啦 唔合格係咪要重考先？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月7號 機場2.0 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知你都知 我地大家都好攰 係唔係？<br />\n但係你仲記唔記得我地有約？<br />\n我地約左係煲底見㗎嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">切勿離隊（無論以任何方式）<br />\n切勿割席（因為好傷手足心）<br />\n切勿互屌（好多時唔啱傾到啱 <br />\n肯聽一定有進步）<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n我真係好攰 我都偷偷地休息左一日陪屋企人<br />\n但係 我唔可以比人覺得我係廢青三分鐘熱度<br />\n<br />\n我 出嚟啦 你呢？會唔會到？<br />\n<br />\n97 98 一齊98<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde50d5024330e0ae68c2dafcde06d19e7d5d68e","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"9898"},{"pid":"7a1e8720be6a1353673ffae1afda9bb4f72ac796","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">97機場2.0</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8e3270a040876fa12f277b981977d60bfbf424a6","tid":1535113,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69befa68a30bd381030fe35a1660dcc91a8f09fe","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">97機場2.0</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c24e9debe1865fc78ee26f5542e9918154b21cec","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">97機場2.0</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"26d562063d5269209c4978c9e9cda6f833a0b722","tid":1535113,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「五 大 訴 求，唾 面 自 乾。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c1c580f5189f294c0cb30aa472804886cb6ed25","tid":1535113,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">97機場2.0</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"850cc35a98cb0266b10e637bd084f6bb4d23185e","tid":1535113,"uid":8880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"